Welcome to
Nayarit > 
Welcome to “Marisqueria Nayarit,” a vibrant Mexican seafood restaurant nestled in the heart of North Charleston, South Carolina.

Step into our inviting space and immerse yourself in the flavors and colors of coastal Mexico. Our warm and welcoming ambiance reflects the spirit of a seaside cantina, where every visit feels like a mini-vacation.

As you settle into your seat, let the aroma of sizzling shrimp, grilled fish, and zesty spices tantalize your senses. Our menu is a celebration of the freshest catch from the sea, expertly prepared with authentic Mexican flair. From traditional ceviches bursting with citrusy goodness to rich and hearty seafood stews, each dish is a testament to our commitment to quality and flavor.

We serve the best seafood in town.

Always fresh at the table.

Friendly and nice service.
